data.description: Adorable single story home with completely remodeled kitchen.  Pantry has tons of storage with pullout shelves.  Upgraded matching appliances.  The master bedroom features a walk in closet.  However, the closet can be reverted to another bedroom.  Greenhouse in backyard goes with the sale.  Solar panels to bring those utility bills down.
